<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="50">2.3. Displaying the bank details in the order history</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Carry out the same settings for the payment method Invoice to display the bank details in the <strong>order history</strong> whenever an order is completed. If you activated the option <strong>Show designated use</strong>, then the order ID will be displayed in the <strong>order history</strong> along with the bank details.</p>
</div>
