<h3 id="270">6.8. Automating SEPA payments</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Set up processes to automate your SEPA payments. Go to <strong>System » Processes</strong> and use the procedures <a href="/en/basics/automation/processes/procedures#400">SEPA Pain001</a> and <a href="/en/basics/automation/processes/procedures#410">SEPA Pain008</a>.</p>
